overview.en: CA token is a highly liquid digital asset based on the global financial market, aimed at creating a global financial asset circulation system within the digital economy to reduce costs and promote financial inclusivity.
overview.zh: CA 代币是一种基于全球金融市场的高流动性加密数字资产，旨在创建一个全球范围内的数字经济金融资产流通系统，以降低成本并促进金融包容性。
